<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 01:09:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>使用 β 葡聚糖通过免疫健康延长寿命 |吉尔·卡纳汉医学博士</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/building-longevity-through-immune-health-with-beta-glucan-jill-carnahan-md</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 01:09:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/building-longevity-through-immune-health-with-beta-glucan-jill-carnahan-md</guid></item><item><title>基于 OCT 鉴别首发急性视神经炎一项针对 111 名 NMOSD 和 MOGAD 患者的国际研究</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/oct-based-differentiation-of-first-acute-optic-neuritisan-international-study-of-111-patients-with-nmosd-and-mogad</link><description>基于 OCT 的首次急性视神经炎鉴别：一项针对 111 名 NMOSD 和 MOGAD 患者的国际研究。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/oct-based-differentiation-of-first-acute-optic-neuritisan-international-study-of-111-patients-with-nmosd-and-mogad5.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 00:54:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/oct-based-differentiation-of-first-acute-optic-neuritisan-international-study-of-111-patients-with-nmosd-and-mogad</guid></item><item><title>物理学家刚刚将玻璃变成了强大的量子安全装置</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/physicists-just-turned-glass-into-a-powerful-quantum-security-device</link><description>科学家们将简单的玻璃变成了强大的量子通信设备，可以保护数据免受未来的量子攻击。该芯片集稳定性、速度和多功能性于一身，可在一个紧凑的系统中处理超安全加密和破纪录的随机数生成。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/physicists-just-turned-glass-into-a-powerful-quantum-security-device.webp" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 00:39:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/physicists-just-turned-glass-into-a-powerful-quantum-security-device</guid></item><item><title>40年来，海湾的“海洋气息”首次消失</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/for-the-first-time-in-40-years-the-oceans-breath-in-the-gulf-has-disappeared</link><description>2025 年，巴拿马湾的季节性上升流在至少 40 年来首次消失，打破了长期存在的海洋格局。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/for-the-first-time-in-40-years-the-oceans-breath-in-the-gulf-has-disappeared.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 00:24:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/for-the-first-time-in-40-years-the-oceans-breath-in-the-gulf-has-disappeared</guid></item><item><title>使用磁性凝胶的更安全、更有效的心房颤动治疗方法可能正在开发中</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-safer-more-effective-atrial-fibrillation-treatment-method-using-magnetic-gel-may-be-on-the-way</link><description>心房颤动是一种常见的心脏病，其特征是心脏上腔快速、不规则的心跳。它是心脏中称为左心耳 (LAA) 的小袋中形成的血栓导致中风的主要原因。虽然存在多种治疗选择，但它们有许多缺点，并且风险往往仍然存在。但现在，研究人员开发出了一种有前途的新疗法，涉及磁性流体。他们的研究发表在《自然》杂志上，描述了大鼠和猪研究的新程序和结果。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-safer-more-effective-atrial-fibrillation-treatment-method-using-magnetic-gel-may-be-on-the-way2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 00:09:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-safer-more-effective-atrial-fibrillation-treatment-method-using-magnetic-gel-may-be-on-the-way</guid></item><item><title>自修复航天器可能会改变未来的任务</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/self-repairing-spacecraft-could-change-future-missions</link><description>由于尖端复合技术，可修复的航天器结构很快就会成为可能。瑞士公司 CompPair 和 CSEM 以及比利时公司 Com&amp;amp;Sens 已与欧洲航天局 (ESA) 合作，改进其用于太空运输的自修复碳纤维产品。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/self-repairing-spacecraft-could-change-future-missions2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 23:54:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/self-repairing-spacecraft-could-change-future-missions</guid></item><item><title>时空是基本的还是突现的？与布莱恩·考克斯</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/is-spacetime-fundamental-or-is-it-emergent-with-brian-cox</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 23:39:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/is-spacetime-fundamental-or-is-it-emergent-with-brian-cox</guid></item><item><title>为什么星系之间的时间流动不同</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/why-time-flows-differently-between-galaxies</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 23:24:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/why-time-flows-differently-between-galaxies</guid></item><item><title>溶酶体缺陷正在成为多种炎症性疾病的一个特征</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/lysosomal-defects-are-emerging-as-a-feature-in-multiple-inflammatory-diseases</link><description>Barbara J. Vilen 及其团队现在发现了活动性狼疮患者的晚期内体和溶酶体 (LEL) 缺陷，并表明 LEL 功能降低可通过慢性 PI3k 活性和 SHP-1/SHIP-1 缺陷促进 SLE： &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/lysosomal-defects-are-emerging-as-a-feature-in-multiple-inflammatory-diseases2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 23:09:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/lysosomal-defects-are-emerging-as-a-feature-in-multiple-inflammatory-diseases</guid></item><item><title>蛋白质图谱连接神经退行性疾病背后的生物点</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/protein-atlas-connects-the-biological-dots-underlying-neurodegenerative-diseases</link><description>神经退行性疾病形成了一个错综复杂的生物网，具有重叠的分子特征和症状。为了解读这种复杂性，由圣裘德儿童研究医院科学家领导的多机构合作开发了泛神经退行性疾病图谱 (PanNDA)。该图谱是对神经退行性疾病“蛋白质组”的全面调查，包含有关蛋白质水平、修饰和相互作用的信息。该资源今天发表在《细胞》杂志上，提供了基于蛋白质的广泛前景，以更好地了解神经退行性疾病的起源并帮助其诊断和治疗。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/protein-atlas-connects-the-biological-dots-underlying-neurodegenerative-diseases2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 22:54:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/protein-atlas-connects-the-biological-dots-underlying-neurodegenerative-diseases</guid></item></channel></rss>